<template><div><h2 id="介绍" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#介绍" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 介绍</h2>
<p><strong>Halo-Theme-Hao</strong> 是一款适用于 <a href="https://github.com/halo-dev/halo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Halo2.0<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 的博客主题</p>
<p>移植自 Hexo 社区 <a href="https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">hexo-theme-butterfly<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>主题中 <a href="https://blog.zhheo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Heo<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 的魔改</p>
<h2 id="安裝" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#安裝" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 安裝</h2>
<p>在 <a href="https://github.com/liuzhihang/halo-theme-hao/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Release<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 页面下载最新版本 zip 后，通过 Halo Console 后台主题安装处上传即可。</p>
